description.narrative: 5.3 Increased capacity to legislate, plan and budget to improve WASH systems, including mainstreaming disaster risk management, which contributes to Children In Urban Settings / Local Governance, Disaster Risk Reduction, Environmental Sustainability, Sanitation, Sanitation (Covid), Water.
